          {
            "title": "Question: Decrementing numbers",
            "id": 72156,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Que montre ce code dans la console ?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" speed = \" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"speed--;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(speed);\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"199\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>199</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>201</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>199</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: += operator",
            "id": 72159,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Ajoute dix à la valeur de la variable en utilisant l'opérateur <code>+=</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" yards = \" /><text value=\"80\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"yards += \" /><text value=\"10\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(yards);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"21\" /><option startIndex=\"22\" endIndex=\"23\" /><option startIndex=\"23\" endIndex=\"24\" /><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"27\" /><option startIndex=\"27\" endIndex=\"28\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"90\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>yards</code> suivi de <code>+</code> puis <code>=</code>, <code>10</code>, <code>;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: -= operator",
            "id": 72160,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Sous-trais 200 de la valeur de la variable en utilisant l'opérateur <code>-=</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" account = \" /><text value=\"1000\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"account -= \" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(account);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"34\" /><option startIndex=\"28\" endIndex=\"30\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"800\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>-=</code> suivi de <code>200</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
